hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張學良得啖笑"},{"pid":"1421d20c0ef893a3d105d6f5dc79f551207312c1","tid":537133,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c8356d498d296afaf350a67563cb835cf58de4","tid":537133,"uid":126590,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>范文虎，張學良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張學良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？奉系打遍東北喎，佢仲自己做埋北洋艦隊的領導人，點廢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"張作霖下話"},{"pid":"9744a16226a31e752bdbb75b4eb4b5878bb8ae89","tid":537133,"uid":88726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5b36e42dc6f4f0b9162ba6399ee25933899e1a2","tid":537133,"uid":17008,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"96dcf921b79ce037a3e8995d402c16cde8e26503","tid":537133,"uid":51625,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"侯景 <br />\n<br />\n自封宇宙大將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T19:34:49.000Z","msg":"依條友比史書寫到幾乎搵唔到一個優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"佢屠殺建康世族，緊係恨之入骨。<br />\n<br />\n對上一次已經係蘇峻之亂"},{"pid":"201b1b6527dacbbe9b7a62a8e7c481f973900546","tid":537133,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e08b30b1d96a3d81c60241d2f7e2369924dbe34","tid":537133,"uid":82175,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"李景隆無得輸<br />\n好似係唯一 俾人下克上 一城之地贏全國 太平時叛亂成功"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"但佢好似開外卦咁 最尾都可以無俾人處死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass